Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:05.06,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这是个世界总人口八成左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.49,0:00:09.86,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,天生拥有“特异体质·个性”的超人社会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:14.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,为了对抗使用个性进行犯罪的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.38,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,“英雄”作为一种职业诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.72,0:00:28.29,MHA.S04.TOP.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,训练场β
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:28.69,MHA.S04.PASS,,0,0,0,,我们雄英高中1年A班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:32.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,为了通过临时执照考试 成为职业英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:34.56,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,开始了救助训练
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:40.10,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,然而 突然发生了原因不明的崩塌事故
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:42.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我们受困于地下街
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.16,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,尝试逃出来的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.35,0:00:50.51,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,在途中与八百万同学 以及负伤的饭田同学会合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:57.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,度过重重危机 到达了通往地上的电梯口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:02.97,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,然而 一切还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,真正的试炼 现在才刚要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:10.83,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没错 从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:24.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}面对一如既往的耀眼光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:27.98,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}你闭上了眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}没人留意的阴暗角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}隐藏着一束光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:38.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}迷茫 困惑 梦中的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:42.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}纵使泪水划过脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}希望让你不再悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.34,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}将惊人一鸣献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:55.76,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}将无法改变的过去涂上颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:59.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}未来定是七彩缤纷 单手拿着调色盘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}展露笑颜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:05.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}这是我一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}仅有的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:10.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}跨过最糟糕的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:14.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}所见无虚 没有误会 不会弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:18.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}为了能真心地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}我的祈祷并非仅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:24.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}也并非转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.42,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}相信定会改变 再度起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:36.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.18}将你逐渐缩小的视野 将我的世界拓宽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:46.02,MHA.S04.TITLE,,0,0,0,,活下去!\N{\fs20}\N {\fs60}殊死的生存训练\N{\fs45}\N {\fs60}后篇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.17,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,阳光照进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:52.47,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,能从这里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:54.59,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,从这里就能回到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,看建筑构造图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:01.41,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,电梯最多只能到地下1层
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:03.57,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,那为什么会有光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.51,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:11.04,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,地上的部分也发生崩塌 所以阳光才照进来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.39,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,那样正好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.17,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:19.78,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,有御茶子的个性 这样就能回到地面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.56,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好 那就让大家飘起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:23.75,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,等一下 丽日同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:29.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,八百万同学 你到地下1层后 能把绳梯放下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:31.08,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.91,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷 你要留下来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.94,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,留下来 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,班上的大家也许还没离开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.34,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,也可能像饭田同学一样受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.56,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我要确认大家平安无事 带他们来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:50.30,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,八百万同学 你们就先送饭田同学避难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:52.32,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.46,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,八百万同学 还要麻烦你向老师们报告情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好 我一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.66,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你要当心哦 绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:09.61,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,出久同学 要是遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我明白 我会马上避难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.30,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.57,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰 为什么紧急照明亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:30.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,应该是有人修好了紧急用电
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.69,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,传送电力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是上鸣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:37.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,应该是有人让上鸣这么做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.72,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,头脑这么机灵的家伙 应该是绿谷和八百万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.76,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,还有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:46.50,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.78,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我找到了 待救援者假人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:51.67,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.61,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你这个臭市民 给我们添了多少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.78,0:04:57.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,回头我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.53,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,宰了假人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:01.06,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,但是 要怎么挖出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:03.53,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,硬拉出一个万一又发生崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.47,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我们也会被活埋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.25,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你说呢 爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:09.17,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:09.99,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:12.51,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你没听到我刚才说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.77,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我觉得我解释得很详细了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:19.14,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你看 这么脆弱 感觉随时都会崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:22.39,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,所以说 在崩塌前救出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:23.63,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:28.45,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,上鸣 如果在那里不是假人 而是活人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.18,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,人家就在那边求救 你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.12,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,因为办不到 就此放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:34.98,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:39.46,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,但是 现在又不是真人 只是训练…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,应该不用勉强去救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.79,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你自有胜算吧 爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.74,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,当然有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.40,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.79,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我们是为了成为英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,才加入雄英的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:54.90,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你说对吧 上鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.88,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,话是这么说 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:06:00.44,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,快开始吧 臭路人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.94,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,至少告诉我有什么计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,从那里就能回到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.42,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,丽日同学 上去后立刻带饭田同学去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:27.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,蛙吹同学也跟着去 并且去向老师报告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.29,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我回去放绳梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.32,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,只有你们逃出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.54,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,相泽老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,准备好了吧 路人们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.62,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,拜托了 可别打到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.56,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,去死吧 AP射击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.97,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,去吧 切岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:57.99,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.13,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:13.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,彻底去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.40,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,什么声音 崩塌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:24.18,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,不 不对 应该是楼下有人破坏了什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.36,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:29.86,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.60,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是爆豪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:37.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,现在随时都可能发生崩塌 这家伙在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.65,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆破声是从下面传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.00,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,地下6层 最下层啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.00,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,偏偏是最脆弱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.71,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,让紧急用电恢复的人是爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.99,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,而且还造成了这样的爆破 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:58.12,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这种情况下他还在继续救援训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:00.28,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.57,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.44,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,都怪你在这种地方那样搞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.44,0:08:12.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:15.06,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,别再拖拖拉拉了 快上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:22.18,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,喂喂 这样下去我们就要淹死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.47,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这下怎么办 爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:32.56,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,“不会去救人”是什么意思 相泽老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.60,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,难道说地下街的崩塌…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:37.45,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是意料之中的意外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:39.46,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.24,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这点危机都无法解决的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.48,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是不可能拿到临时执照的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.81,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,可是 饭田同学都受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.05,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,其他人可能也被困在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.31,0:08:54.70,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,那么 他们就不再是英雄 是待救援者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:56.58,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,谁能去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我去准备绳梯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:08:59.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.73,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是不是做的太过火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.97,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我做好了以防万一的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:14.16,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,常暗 用黑影破坏地板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:16.97,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,可是 这么黑我无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.11,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,用我的火焰来压制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.27,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:22.82,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.18,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.49,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:37.07,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.61,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:40.04,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:42.31,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,谁要你帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.71,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这种情况下你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:48.81,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,就让人家帮忙吧 接受轰的好意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:50.73,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,快点 抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.58,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆豪 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.41,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,别拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:54.72,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:09:59.83,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.16,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,多谢了 轰 常暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.66,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.99,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没时间放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:10.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,地下水还没有止住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.05,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我来冻住水流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这段时间你们快逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:17.69,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰 我也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:21.11,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你们几个的个性无法对付这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.82,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,靠太近还会被冻结波及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.82,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,不想拖后腿就赶快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:29.53,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.58,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,现在要争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:32.81,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,赶快逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.26,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.24,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,耍什么帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:37.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我在上面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:38.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.46,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这么大的空间 不知道我能冻结到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:57.02,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,至少要争取到 让他们逃走的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.24,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 温度下降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.70,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是轰同学在用冻结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.12,0:11:16.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是为了控制住崩塌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.55,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,总之 我要赶快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.03,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,只能使用强硬手段了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.27,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:33.43,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,切岛同学 上鸣同学 常暗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,太好了 你们平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.47,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,嗯 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.89,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,大家一直往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:43.07,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,在那座打开的电梯里面有绳梯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.67,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这样就能回到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.51,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.94,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我们得救了啊 切岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:48.67,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.70,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,常暗同学 轰同学还在下面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:57.05,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,他在用冻结阻止地下水涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,用冻结阻止地下水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:00.87,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.06,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,就差一点了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.38,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没有绳梯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.32,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.53,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,切岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.85,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,还有上鸣的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.47,0:12:19.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,切岛同学 上鸣同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.48,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这个声音是 丽日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:26.07,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,对我现在放绳梯下去 你们再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.43,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:30.41,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,做绳梯的是八百万吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.69,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你应该很累了 抱歉 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:39.49,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,当 当然了 要继续迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:47.16,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,总算是阻止了地下水的上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.86,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,但比起这个 你为什么还在这里 爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.00,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我不想欠你人情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:55.16,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,怎样都好 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.30,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.73,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,现在逃也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.19,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,就算轰同学的冻结再怎么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:09.09,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,也不可能冻住这么一大片场地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:15.02,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,应该只是冻住了水面几公分 不 十几公分的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:18.82,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,下面应该承受了流进来的地下水的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:25.21,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这样一来 被压迫水 就会从墙壁的裂缝中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:28.49,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,像水箭一样把砖块炸开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.54,0:13:32.96,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的情况 地下街可能会整个崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,当然 我也已经预测到这种情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:37.78,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,少放马后炮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.96,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,但你还是留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:44.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜留下来 是为了救助轰同学 而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:50.01,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜一定已经想好了逃离的对策
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.36,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜 你会怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:56.53,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你要怎么救他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.30,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你已经想好了逃生方法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:03.00,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,给我听好了 半边混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.93,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我现在爆破冰块开个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.02,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,制造间歇泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.91,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,水就会涌出
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:16.47,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰同学就顺势将水的表面冻结 制造立足点向上升
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:22.36,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我朝着上面 不断爆破把天花板打穿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:26.22,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这样就能一口气到上面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.21,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我理解你的逃生方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:33.95,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,但是你的爆破 能这么精准打开让水喷出来的洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.19,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:39.62,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,不 就算是小胜 成功概率也很低
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:45.24,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,但是 我的射门式就能打开所需的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.89,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,发目同学制作的战斗服γ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.79,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,只要靠它的耐久力 把ONE FOR ALL的比率提升到极限
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.07,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜 轰同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:14:59.16,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:02.26,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你来干什么 臭呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.09,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我负责在冰上开洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.04,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:07.57,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰同学 做好冻结准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:08.43,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.97,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜准备好爆破天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:13.27,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,别对我指手画脚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.01,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没时间了 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:23.56,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,ONE FOR ALL 全覆盖 5%
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.27,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆碎风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:36.38,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:40.92,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,下一波要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:46.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:52.93,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:00.98,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,-上鸣同学 -上鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:03.22,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,常暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:04.76,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,来这边 上鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.73,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:10.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:11.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.13,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 小梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:21.15,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.87,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,太好了 你醒了 饭田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.19,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,八百万同学 我到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,训练中地下街发生崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.63,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.79,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:41.83,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是你把受伤的我送回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.11,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.74,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,该道谢的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.44,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.91,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,客气什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:53.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,其他同学呢 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.40,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:59.96,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,切岛同学 上鸣同学 常暗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:02.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,丽日同学 蛙吹同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.34,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,叫我小梅雨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.01,0:17:07.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小梅雨同学 你们没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:12.05,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷同学 爆豪同学他们人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:18.11,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是这样的 最下层突然涌进了地下水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.41,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰用冻结争取了逃生时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.75,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆豪也留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:28.28,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷知道后就去救他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.48,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.62,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,也就是说 他们三个都还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:35.93,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.24,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,出久同学回去救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:41.08,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,一定是有信心能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:46.18,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,而且 爆豪同学和轰同学 也不会被这种小危机打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:49.61,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,所以 他们一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:51.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:56.15,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,好 在这里的人一起成立救助小组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:18:00.15,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,能拜托你们吗 切岛同学 丽日同学 小梅雨同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:00.81,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.42,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,一定救出他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.03,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,他们几个一定在往上面走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:07.69,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,从地下二层开始找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:24.83,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:32.17,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,绿谷 振作点 绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:39.53,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,轰同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.09,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:46.49,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,撞得全身都在痛 不过 还能动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:48.54,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这里是第几层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.80,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我们是在破坏3次天花板后掉下来的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.25,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,所以这里应该是地下3层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.72,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这样啊 那争取到不少距离了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:19:00.06,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这样就能在地下水淹上来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.60,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,回到地面上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.36,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,都要感谢轰同学 还有小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:07.12,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.37,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:12.58,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.18,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆豪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.09,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.93,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜 振作点 小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:31.55,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,别在我耳边哇哇叫 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.99,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,爆豪 抓住我和绿谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.43,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我们从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:41.11,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这点小伤 不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:42.64,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,别勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.98,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我才不用你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:49.61,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜 没时间了 抓住我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:50.57,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.88,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.32,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,就算勉强我也要做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.62,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,这点事都要人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.86,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,还怎么成为No.1英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.82,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你都站不稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.17,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,只是扭到脚了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:09.83,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜 抓着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,放开我 臭久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:12.20,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.35,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我也想救你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:19.17,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,恢复备用电源的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:22.33,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,而且 还是为了让大家方便逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:26.55,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,不对 我只是为了快点找到该死的待救援者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.96,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,那为什么要留到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:31.90,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,因为你想救轰同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.30,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我不想欠人情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.85,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我被小胜救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.39,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,嗯 我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:42.04,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,所以 只是现在也好 让我们帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.88,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.50,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:48.61,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,小胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.45,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,当我的拐杖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:20:58.23,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:02.62,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,为了让我能自己能走 当我的拐杖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:06.15,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,嗯 我会的 当你的拐杖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:07.67,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,拐杖就别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.38,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.55,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你现在不就在说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.49,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,你在说什么 我听不懂啦 臭呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.60,0:21:21.27,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,快到了 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.48,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.93,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,都叫你不准说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.02,0:21:25.85,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,找到他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.52,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:30.91,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,在临时执照考试前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:34.58,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,我会在你们面前筑起数道高墙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:38.87,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,跨越过去吧 勇往直前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.84,0:21:41.46,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,前往更遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.55,MHA.S04.DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,继续迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:08.85,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}从何时起我变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:13.90,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}越来越擅长忍耐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:23.62,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}{\fad(0,350)}儿时还曾被说是爱哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:30.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:34.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}{\fad(0,350)}多么残酷的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:40.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}呐喊声逐渐模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:46.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}与本应平淡无奇的未来渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.64,0:22:51.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}谁人都知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:57.19,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}我无法到达他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.28,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}那要走到哪里才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:08.37,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}不知道答案 只能紧紧抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.37,0:23:11.29,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}那股能消除不安的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:17.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fax-0.2}在心中不断升温 永不消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:19.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\blur2\fax-0.2}我想改变
